description:
On today’s show, Emily is joined by sex and intimacy coach John Wineland to talk about sexual energy, consent, and understanding both.

They discuss masculine and feminine energies as the foundation to deeper sex – regardless of who you’re sleeping with, being a more conscious partner and lover, and why learning the difference between “no” and “not yet” can make a world of difference in the bedroom.
